description: GsmSector: GSM sector-level data containing timestamps, location, identifiers, data type information, and BSC (Base Station Controller) details.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp), Area_Name (geographic area), CellId (cell identifier), Id2 (duplicate cell identifier), Id3 (alternative cell identifier), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (data format version), GsmSector.gsmSectorId (GSM sector ID), GsmSector.userLabel (user-defined label), GsmSector.bscTgIdentity (BSC transceiver group identity), GsmSector.bscNodeIdentity (BSC node identity).
